<plot>Perry is a likeable enough guy with quirky tastes and a rather sad track record in the ways of the heart. Alice is his best friend, a sharp, artistic woman with a heartbreaking past -- one she still hasn't come to grips with. Morgan is a blunt, striking goth-chick who knows the effect she has on men and how to use it to her advantage. When Perry meets Morgan at a party, it sets off a fateful path for the trio, fueled by raging hormones, painful secrets and unexpected violence.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?011166</url></doc>
